{"label": "droite", "transcript": [{"text": "La question du renouvellement", "start": 0.283, "duration": 1.083}, {"text": "de la flotte est sans doute", "start": 1.366, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "l'une des questions", "start": 3.766, "duration": 0.784}, {"text": "les plus d\u00e9solantes", "start": 4.55, "duration": 2.6}, {"text": "que nous ayons eues", "start": 7.15, "duration": 0.75}, {"text": "\u00e0 traiter,", "start": 7.9, "duration": 0.7}, {"text": "et \u00e0 traiter \u00e0 nouveau,", "start": 8.6, "duration": 1.2}, {"text": "au cours de ce mandat.", "start": 9.8, "duration": 0.9}, {"text": "D\u00e9solante parce que,", "start": 10.7, "duration": 1.433}, {"text": "depuis des ann\u00e9es maintenant,", "start": 12.133, "duration": 1.117}, {"text": "le Parlement a fait un choix clair", "start": 13.25, "duration": 1.35}, {"text": "- et m\u00eame nos pr\u00e9d\u00e9cesseurs", "start": 14.6, "duration": 2.716}, {"text": "ont vot\u00e9 ici", "start": 17.316, "duration": 1.184}, {"text": "au cours du dernier mandat", "start": 18.5, "duration": 0.95}, {"text": "- pour demander que soient", "start": 19.45, "duration": 3.25}, {"text": "enfin lib\u00e9r\u00e9s", "start": 22.7, "duration": 0.866}, {"text": "les moyens n\u00e9cessaires", "start": 23.566, "duration": 1.2}, {"text": "pour soutenir", "start": 24.766, "duration": 0.534}, {"text": "le renouvellement", "start": 25.3, "duration": 0.516}, {"text": "de la flotte", "start": 25.816, "duration": 0.384}, {"text": "dans les r\u00e9gions ultrap\u00e9riph\u00e9riques.", "start": 26.2, "duration": 2.05}, {"text": "Et aujourd'hui", "start": 28.25, "duration": 0.566}, {"text": "encore, nous en sommes", "start": 28.816, "duration": 0.867}, {"text": "au m\u00eame point,", "start": 29.683, "duration": 1.267}, {"text": "\u00e0 des r\u00e9ponses", "start": 30.95, "duration": 0.616}, {"text": "qui, finalement, n'arrivent jamais", "start": 31.566, "duration": 1.934}, {"text": "\u00e0 la conclusion n\u00e9cessaire,", "start": 33.5, "duration": 1.8}, {"text": "et \u00e0 des man\u0153uvres dilatoires", "start": 35.3, "duration": 2.183}, {"text": "qui ne cessent de retarder", "start": 37.483, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "le fait que soient enfin", "start": 39.55, "duration": 1.45}, {"text": "mis sur la table", "start": 41.0, "duration": 0.9}, {"text": "les fonds dont les p\u00eacheurs", "start": 41.9, "duration": 1.433}, {"text": "ont besoin", "start": 43.333, "duration": 0.517}, {"text": "pour renouveler leur flotte.", "start": 43.85, "duration": 1.433}, {"text": "Vous l'avez dit,", "start": 45.283, "duration": 0.367}, {"text": "Monsieur le Pr\u00e9sident,", "start": 45.65, "duration": 0.616}, {"text": "nous parlons ici de s\u00e9curit\u00e9.", "start": 46.266, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "Nous parlons de la vie", "start": 48.666, "duration": 1.05}, {"text": "et de la mort", "start": 49.716, "duration": 0.884}, {"text": "de ceux qui vont en mer", "start": 50.6, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "pour pouvoir nourrir", "start": 52.666, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "les Europ\u00e9ens.", "start": 55.0, "duration": 1.466}, {"text": "Nous parlons aussi", "start": 56.466, "duration": 1.417}, {"text": "de l'attractivit\u00e9 du m\u00e9tier", "start": 57.883, "duration": 1.567}, {"text": "et du renouvellement", "start": 59.45, "duration": 0.716}, {"text": "de la flotte.", "start": 60.166, "duration": 0.484}, {"text": "Nous parlons", "start": 60.65, "duration": 1.05}, {"text": "du confort \u00e0 bord", "start": 61.7, "duration": 1.066}, {"text": "qui est", "start": 62.766, "duration": 0.75}, {"text": "\u00e9videmment n\u00e9cessaire.", "start": 63.516, "duration": 1.084}, {"text": "Nous parlons", "start": 64.6, "duration": 0.933}, {"text": "donc de la capacit\u00e9", "start": 65.533, "duration": 1.167}, {"text": "\u00e0 continuer", "start": 66.7, "duration": 0.566}, {"text": "de produire dans nos pays.", "start": 67.266, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "Vous disiez,", "start": 69.366, "duration": 0.334}, {"text": "Monsieur le Pr\u00e9sident,", "start": 69.7, "duration": 0.633}, {"text": "si les bateaux", "start": 70.333, "duration": 1.417}, {"text": "ne sont pas renouvel\u00e9s,", "start": 71.75, "duration": 0.95}, {"text": "alors ce sont", "start": 72.7, "duration": 0.55}, {"text": "des fili\u00e8res enti\u00e8res", "start": 73.25, "duration": 0.8}, {"text": "qui vont s'effondrer,", "start": 74.05, "duration": 0.716}, {"text": "qui ne seront pas remplac\u00e9es.", "start": 74.766, "duration": 1.5}, {"text": "Elles seront en r\u00e9alit\u00e9", "start": 76.266, "duration": 1.75}, {"text": "\u00e9videmment", "start": 78.016, "duration": 0.934}, {"text": "remplac\u00e9es par", "start": 78.95, "duration": 0.65}, {"text": "les importations.", "start": 79.6, "duration": 1.233}, {"text": "Elles seront remplac\u00e9es", "start": 80.833, "duration": 0.9}, {"text": "par une p\u00eache", "start": 81.733, "duration": 0.817}, {"text": "que nous importons.", "start": 82.55, "duration": 1.4}, {"text": "Et cette p\u00eache-l\u00e0,", "start": 83.95, "duration": 1.8}, {"text": "La Commission sait-elle", "start": 85.75, "duration": 1.0}, {"text": "qui est massivement", "start": 86.75, "duration": 0.766}, {"text": "subventionn\u00e9e ?", "start": 87.516, "duration": 1.417}, {"text": "Prenons l'exemple simple", "start": 88.933, "duration": 1.5}, {"text": "de la R\u00e9union, de Mayotte :", "start": 90.433, "duration": 1.917}, {"text": "Comment ne pas voir", "start": 92.35, "duration": 0.85}, {"text": "que, dans l'oc\u00e9an", "start": 93.2, "duration": 0.6}, {"text": "Indien, aujourd'hui, partout,", "start": 93.8, "duration": 1.166}, {"text": "nous voyons", "start": 94.966, "duration": 0.9}, {"text": "une p\u00eache chinoise,", "start": 95.866, "duration": 1.234}, {"text": "une p\u00eache indienne,", "start": 97.1, "duration": 1.216}, {"text": "une p\u00eache iranienne,", "start": 98.316, "duration": 1.334}, {"text": "une p\u00eache africaine", "start": 99.65, "duration": 1.283}, {"text": "qui sont en r\u00e9alit\u00e9", "start": 100.933, "duration": 1.317}, {"text": "largement \u00e9quip\u00e9es par", "start": 102.25, "duration": 1.266}, {"text": "des moyens publics,", "start": 103.516, "duration": 1.2}, {"text": "y compris, et c'est l\u00e0", "start": 105.766, "duration": 1.617}, {"text": "le sujet de r\u00e9volte", "start": 107.383, "duration": 1.467}, {"text": "le plus absolu, des p\u00eacheurs", "start": 108.85, "duration": 1.15}, {"text": "europ\u00e9ens par des moyens", "start": 110.0, "duration": 1.2}, {"text": "publics europ\u00e9ens.", "start": 111.2, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "J'ai \u00e9t\u00e9 rapporteur", "start": 113.533, "duration": 1.05}, {"text": "pour l'accord de p\u00eache", "start": 114.583, "duration": 0.983}, {"text": "que nous avons", "start": 115.566, "duration": 0.634}, {"text": "renouvel\u00e9 r\u00e9cemment", "start": 116.2, "duration": 1.05}, {"text": "avec l'\u00eele Maurice.", "start": 117.25, "duration": 1.5}, {"text": "Dans cet accord de p\u00eache,", "start": 118.75, "duration": 1.083}, {"text": "la Commission europ\u00e9enne,", "start": 119.833, "duration": 0.933}, {"text": "l'Union europ\u00e9enne,", "start": 120.766, "duration": 1.134}, {"text": "met \u00e0 disposition", "start": 121.9, "duration": 1.05}, {"text": "des p\u00eacheurs mauriciens", "start": 122.95, "duration": 0.9}, {"text": "des moyens pour", "start": 123.85, "duration": 1.766}, {"text": "renouveler leur flotte.", "start": 125.616, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "Donc les p\u00eacheurs", "start": 127.816, "duration": 0.95}, {"text": "de la R\u00e9union,", "start": 128.766, "duration": 0.75}, {"text": "les p\u00eacheurs de Mayotte", "start": 129.516, "duration": 1.567}, {"text": "auxquels la Commission interdit", "start": 131.083, "duration": 1.917}, {"text": "de recourir \u00e0 des fonds", "start": 133.0, "duration": 1.5}, {"text": "que m\u00eame nos \u00c9tats", "start": 134.5, "duration": 0.85}, {"text": "seraient pr\u00eats", "start": 135.35, "duration": 0.466}, {"text": "\u00e0 mettre sur la table", "start": 135.816, "duration": 0.667}, {"text": "pour les aider", "start": 136.483, "duration": 0.817}, {"text": "\u00e0 investir dans leur avenir,", "start": 137.3, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "voient arriver", "start": 139.333, "duration": 0.817}, {"text": "dans leurs eaux,", "start": 140.15, "duration": 0.95}, {"text": "dans nos eaux,", "start": 141.1, "duration": 0.666}, {"text": "dans les eaux", "start": 141.766, "duration": 0.484}, {"text": "internationales,", "start": 142.25, "duration": 1.066}, {"text": "des bateaux", "start": 143.316, "duration": 0.9}, {"text": "neufs financ\u00e9s", "start": 144.216, "duration": 1.334}, {"text": "avec des fonds europ\u00e9ens", "start": 145.55, "duration": 1.55}, {"text": "qui leur sont \u00e0 eux refus\u00e9s.", "start": 147.1, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "Comment est-ce que c'est", "start": 149.683, "duration": 1.267}, {"text": "possible de comprendre", "start": 150.95, "duration": 0.983}, {"text": "une telle contradiction ?", "start": 151.933, "duration": 0.783}, {"text": "Alors on nous dit", "start": 152.716, "duration": 0.784}, {"text": "il y a la dimension", "start": 153.5, "duration": 0.716}, {"text": "environnementale,", "start": 154.216, "duration": 0.65}, {"text": "il y a l'impact", "start": 154.866, "duration": 0.584}, {"text": "environnemental ;", "start": 155.45, "duration": 0.566}, {"text": "Il y a les infos", "start": 156.016, "duration": 1.55}, {"text": "sur les subventions", "start": 157.566, "duration": 0.85}, {"text": "dangereuses", "start": 158.416, "duration": 0.484}, {"text": "pour l'environnement ;", "start": 158.9, "duration": 0.75}, {"text": "Mais nous ne parlons pas", "start": 159.65, "duration": 0.65}, {"text": "d'augmenter", "start": 160.3, "duration": 0.483}, {"text": "l'effort de p\u00eache !", "start": 160.783, "duration": 1.117}, {"text": "Nous parlons seulement", "start": 161.9, "duration": 0.683}, {"text": "de la possibilit\u00e9", "start": 162.583, "duration": 0.75}, {"text": "de le poursuivre.", "start": 163.333, "duration": 1.417}, {"text": "Et surtout, nous parlons", "start": 164.75, "duration": 0.716}, {"text": "d'une p\u00eache,", "start": 165.466, "duration": 0.684}, {"text": "et je termine par l\u00e0,", "start": 166.15, "duration": 0.85}, {"text": "dont l'impact", "start": 167.0, "duration": 0.466}, {"text": "est de toute fa\u00e7on", "start": 167.466, "duration": 0.784}, {"text": "tr\u00e8s modeste.", "start": 168.25, "duration": 1.116}, {"text": "Comment est-ce qu'on peut", "start": 169.366, "duration": 0.6}, {"text": "expliquer \u00e0 des p\u00eacheurs", "start": 169.966, "duration": 1.0}, {"text": "- prenez par exemple", "start": 170.966, "duration": 0.917}, {"text": "sur la flotte thoni\u00e8re,", "start": 171.883, "duration": 1.233}, {"text": "dont la totalit\u00e9", "start": 173.116, "duration": 1.017}, {"text": "des captures autoris\u00e9e", "start": 174.133, "duration": 1.05}, {"text": "est 30 tonnes par an, 30", "start": 175.183, "duration": 3.233}, {"text": "tonnes de thon", "start": 179.05, "duration": 1.15}, {"text": "albacore par an -", "start": 180.2, "duration": 1.433}, {"text": "qu'on ne veuille", "start": 181.633, "duration": 0.817}, {"text": "pas renouveler", "start": 182.45, "duration": 0.8}, {"text": "leur flotte", "start": 184.633, "duration": 0.967}, {"text": "alors que les senneurs europ\u00e9ens", "start": 185.6, "duration": 1.166}, {"text": "ont droit au total", "start": 186.766, "duration": 0.65}, {"text": "\u00e0 73\u202f000 tonnes.", "start": 187.416, "duration": 1.934}, {"text": "\u00c9videmment, ce n'est pas l\u00e0", "start": 189.35, "duration": 0.95}, {"text": "que se trouve", "start": 190.3, "duration": 0.416}, {"text": "le probl\u00e8me environnemental.", "start": 190.716, "duration": 0.934}, {"text": "Donc nous commettons", "start": 191.65, "duration": 1.416}, {"text": "un contresens \u00e9conomique,", "start": 193.066, "duration": 2.15}, {"text": "un contresens g\u00e9opolitique", "start": 195.733, "duration": 1.867}, {"text": "et une faute majeure", "start": 197.6, "duration": 1.366}, {"text": "contre le choix d\u00e9mocratique", "start": 198.966, "duration": 1.334}, {"text": "du Parlement", "start": 200.3, "duration": 0.533}, {"text": "et des institutions europ\u00e9ennes,", "start": 200.833, "duration": 1.317}, {"text": "une faute majeure", "start": 202.15, "duration": 0.816}, {"text": "contre les p\u00eacheurs europ\u00e9ens.", "start": 202.966, "duration": 2.1}, {"text": "Et c'est en leur nom,", "start": 205.066, "duration": 0.6}, {"text": "je crois, qu'il est temps,", "start": 205.666, "duration": 1.1}, {"text": "maintenant, que nous sortions", "start": 206.766, "duration": 1.417}, {"text": "des discours qui tournent", "start": 208.183, "duration": 2.7}, {"text": "autour du probl\u00e8me", "start": 210.883, "duration": 0.783}, {"text": "pour aller enfin", "start": 211.666, "duration": 1.134}, {"text": "\u00e0 la r\u00e9solution.", "start": 212.8, "duration": 0.666}, {"text": "Nous esp\u00e9rons que", "start": 213.466, "duration": 1.05}, {"text": "dans les prochains jours,", "start": 214.516, "duration": 0.717}, {"text": "dans les prochaines semaines,", "start": 215.233, "duration": 0.717}, {"text": "avant la fin de ce mandat,", "start": 215.95, "duration": 1.083}, {"text": "en tous les cas,", "start": 217.033, "duration": 1.117}, {"text": "nous aurons de", "start": 218.15, "duration": 0.616}, {"text": "la part de la Commission", "start": 218.766, "duration": 0.85}, {"text": "enfin une vraie r\u00e9ponse", "start": 219.616, "duration": 1.4}, {"text": "qui ne soit pas", "start": 221.016, "duration": 0.4}, {"text": "seulement l'ajout de lignes", "start": 221.416, "duration": 0.9}, {"text": "directrices suppl\u00e9mentaires,", "start": 222.316, "duration": 0.934}, {"text": "mais une r\u00e9ponse concr\u00e8te", "start": 223.25, "duration": 1.35}, {"text": "pour permettre", "start": 224.6, "duration": 0.6}, {"text": "de d\u00e9bloquer ces fonds", "start": 225.2, "duration": 0.866}, {"text": "qui sont attendus avec tant", "start": 226.066, "duration": 1.584}, {"text": "d'urgence par les p\u00eacheurs", "start": 227.65, "duration": 0.933}, {"text": "europ\u00e9ens. Merci beaucoup.", "start": 228.583, "duration": 0.967}]}